{"type": "article", "id": 7765, "title": "宜家要给全世界难民一万个临时避难所", "description": "他们说，即使是避难也要避得舒适且有尊严。", "date": "2015-03-26T07:53:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 1277, "name": "IKEA"}, {"id": 8198, "name": "避难所"}, {"id": 1277, "name": "IKEA"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061559276KfBVtPiyaq57XZO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t宜家家居旗下的慈善组织宜家基金会（The IKEA Foundation）此前宣布他们联合联合国难民署（United Nations Refugee Agency，即 UNHCR）设计了一款难民临时避难所，经过在阿拉伯地区 40 多个家庭的试验和改进，现在已经投入生产，计划生产一万座。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t这项设计名为 “Better Shelter”，采用的是宜家的扁平设计，整个“房子”采用金属管钢架搭建，而板材则采用的是轻质的塑料板。此外，屋顶上安置了可拆卸的太阳能电池板，可以为难民提供方便的电力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155923Zze0aIxdAhgEcyqR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061559236DwTga2JGZCkMuR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t这个难民所可以快速被搭建，一般只需要 4 个小时便可以完成，且不需要依赖别的工具。搭建完成后占地面积约为 17.5 平米，可供 5 个人居住。比起传统的帐篷等，宜家避难所为难民提供的不只有舒适，还有隐私尊重和个人空间的保护。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155924ZUzAlW8OyK5gX9HD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5534188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155924WR8v7w1GqJlYkacK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6517094\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155925x5Te71jp09GViPsO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76923077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">此外，随着时间的推移和材料的老化，难民所可以不断被完善和更新，比如添加土墙，更换屋顶等。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t2014 年，这项设计获得了瑞典设计大奖，当时的大赛评委，也是设计评论家 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/03/24/ikea-flat-pack-refugee-shelters-go-into-production-better-shelter-unhcr/\" target=\"_blank\">Alice Rawsthorn 表示</a>，这项设计是一次拥有“不同寻常敏感和智慧的反应”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155925b7f9TRnUgA8t5Dwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155926XsT5iIraSOR3zcBD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155926KTZG0oa9qzCpEHwA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tUNHCR 住房和难民安置署主席 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/03/24/ikea-flat-pack-refugee-shelters-go-into-production-better-shelter-unhcr/\" target=\"_blank\">Shaun Scales 表示</a>，难民住房计划是人道主义庇护的重要发展，宜家的临时难民所也为难民安置提供了新的选择，将会显著改善因危机和灾难而流离失所的人们的生命。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t图片来自：<em><a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/03/24/ikea-flat-pack-refugee-shelters-go-into-production-better-shelter-unhcr/\" target=\"_blank\">Dezeen</a></em> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}